---
title: Shrimp Linguine With a Kick with Garlic Herb Butter and Zucchini
description: These are some fightin’ shrimp: in this dish, the shellfish are given a feisty kick by slices of Thai chili. That’s sure to please heat-lovers, but you can always make adjustments if you prefer to walk on the mild side. Toss in zucchini, garlic herb butter, Parmesan, and al dente pasta, and everything comes together in a savory, spicy, and piping-hot pile of perfection on your plate.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/shrimp-pasta-with-a-kick-369c9223.jpg
